{{menutrail|Main menu|Options menu|Sound options}}
The '''OpenAL options''' menu allows to change settings exclusive to the [[OpenAL]] sound backend. Its [[MENUDEF]] name is {{c|OpenALSoundItems}}.


*'''{{LE|OPENALMNU_PLAYBACKDEVICE}}}''' (Default/<system-dependent list>)
:{{c|{{CVAR|S|snd_aldevice}}}}
:Chooses which audio device to output to.

*'''{{LE|OPENALMNU_ENABLEEFX}}''' (On/Off)
:{{c|{{CVAR|S|snd_efx}}}}
:Allows to enable or disable OpenAL's "Effects Extension" system, a set of effects similar to {{wp|Environmental Audio Extensions|EAX}}, which include notably [[reverbs]].

